	(text "# TODO\n- TP everything!\n\n- LSM6DSV (accel + gyro)\n- LIS2MDL (magnetometer)\n\n- BQ25620 / BQ25601D, batterycharger, logic voltage?\n- TPS61235 (SYS -> 5V) logic voltage?\n- TPS7A2033 3V3 gnss rail\n- BQ27427 battery fuel gauge\n\n- TXS0102 logic lvl shifter\n\n- debug ublox connector\n\n- use I2C 1 + 2\n\n- WATCH FOR INVERSE PINS WHEN SWITCHING SIDE FOR CAM 0 / 1\n\n- transfer SOM based MIPI to CAM connection via FPC\n\n- LIS2MDL DATAREADY pin to gpio"
